NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
Extension 0..*ExtensionProperties of a substance specific to it being a polymer
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:class 0..1ExtensionOverall type of the polymer
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptOverall type of the polymer
extension:geometry 0..1ExtensionPolymer geometry, e.g. linear, branched, cross-linked, network or dendritic
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptPolymer geometry, e.g. linear, branched, cross-linked, network or dendritic
extension:copolymerConnectivity 0..*ExtensionDescrtibes the copolymer sequence type (polymer connectivity)
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptDescrtibes the copolymer sequence type (polymer connectivity)
extension:modification 0..1ExtensionTodo - this is intended to connect to a repeating full modification structure, also used by Protein and Nucleic Acid . String is just a placeholder
value[x] 0..1stringTodo - this is intended to connect to a repeating full modification structure, also used by Protein and Nucleic Acid . String is just a placeholder
extension:monomerSet 0..*ExtensionTodo
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:ratioType 0..1ExtensionCaptures the type of ratio to the entire polymer, e.g. Monomer/Polymer ratio, SRU/Polymer Ratio
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptCaptures the type of ratio to the entire polymer, e.g. Monomer/Polymer ratio, SRU/Polymer Ratio
extension:startingMaterial 0..*ExtensionThe starting materials - monomer(s) used in the synthesis of the polymer
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:code 0..1ExtensionThe type of substance for this starting material
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptThe type of substance for this starting material
extension:category 0..1ExtensionSubstance high level category, e.g. chemical substance
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptSubstance high level category, e.g. chemical substance
extension:isDefining 0..1ExtensionUsed to specify whether the attribute described is a defining element for the unique identification of the polymer
value[x] 0..1booleanUsed to specify whether the attribute described is a defining element for the unique identification of the polymer
extension:amount 0..1ExtensionA percentage
value[x] 0..1QuantityA percentage
extension:repeat 0..*ExtensionSpecifies and quantifies the repeated units and their configuration
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:averageMolecularFormula 0..1ExtensionA representation of an (average) molecular formula from a polymer
value[x] 0..1stringA representation of an (average) molecular formula from a polymer
extension:repeatUnitAmountType 0..1ExtensionHow the quantitative amount of Structural Repeat Units is captured (e.g. Exact, Numeric, Average)
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptHow the quantitative amount of Structural Repeat Units is captured (e.g. Exact, Numeric, Average)
extension:repeatUnit 0..*ExtensionAn SRU - Structural Repeat Unit
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:unit 0..1ExtensionStructural repeat units are essential elements for defining polymers
value[x] 0..1stringStructural repeat units are essential elements for defining polymers
extension:orientation 0..1ExtensionThe orientation of the polymerisation, e.g. head-tail, head-head, random
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptThe orientation of the polymerisation, e.g. head-tail, head-head, random
extension:amount 0..1ExtensionNumber of repeats of this unit
value[x] 0..1integerNumber of repeats of this unit
extension:degreeOfPolymerisation 0..*ExtensionApplies to homopolymer and block co-polymers where the degree of polymerisation within a block can be described
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:type 0..1ExtensionThe type of the degree of polymerisation shall be described, e.g. SRU/Polymer Ratio
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptThe type of the degree of polymerisation shall be described, e.g. SRU/Polymer Ratio
extension:average 0..1ExtensionAn average amount of polymerisation
value[x] 0..1integerAn average amount of polymerisation
extension:low 0..1ExtensionA low expected limit of the amount
value[x] 0..1integerA low expected limit of the amount
extension:high 0..1ExtensionA high expected limit of the amount
value[x] 0..1integerA high expected limit of the amount
extension:structuralRepresentation 0..*ExtensionA graphical structure for this SRU
Slices for extension 0..*ExtensionExtension
Slice: Unordered, Closed by value:url
extension:type 0..1ExtensionThe type of structure (e.g. Full, Partial, Representative)
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptThe type of structure (e.g. Full, Partial, Representative)
extension:representation 0..1ExtensionThe structural representation as text string in a standard format e.g. InChI, SMILES, MOLFILE, CDX, SDF, PDB, mmCIF
value[x] 0..1stringThe structural representation as text string in a standard format e.g. InChI, SMILES, MOLFILE, CDX, SDF, PDB, mmCIF
extension:format 0..1ExtensionThe format of the representation e.g. InChI, SMILES, MOLFILE, CDX, SDF, PDB, mmCIF
value[x] 0..1CodeableConceptThe format of the representation e.g. InChI, SMILES, MOLFILE, CDX, SDF, PDB, mmCIF
extension:attachment 0..1ExtensionAn attached file with the structural representation
value[x] 0..1AttachmentAn attached file with the structural representation
url 1..1uri"http://hl7.org/fhir/5.0/StructureDefinition/extension-SubstancePolymer"
